{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":576670,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"绝了","timestamp":1605763869,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":576677,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"学废了学废了","timestamp":1605763908,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":576683,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈","timestamp":1605763933,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":576695,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"此处3个概率和X系和任何真实院系以及现实中清华大学中坏人的比率，都是洞主编的，大家不要信以为真！","timestamp":1605764046,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":576703,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"简 单 数 学","timestamp":1605764093,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":576746,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"老师好 好坏度是不是可以应该建模成一个正态随机变量更合理一点","timestamp":1605764431,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":576765,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":120176,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 这位同学的思路很好，就留作课后习题同学自己探索一下吧！","timestamp":1605764613,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":6,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":120176,"reply":7,"tag":null,"text":"简单数学应用\n假设你清1000个人里1一个人坏坏的，这个概率，我们记为P（Bad）=1/1000\n如果在每10个坏坏的人里，1个人是X系的，这个概率，我们记为P（X｜Bad）=1/10\n那么一个人既是X系又是坏坏的的概率，我们记为P（X，Bad）=P（X｜Bad）P（Bad）=1/10000\n在你清，100个人里有5个X系的，这个概率我们记为P（X）=5/100\n那么使用贝叶斯定律，我们可以知道，X系中出坏人的概率是P（Bad｜X）=P（X，Bad）/P（X）=0.2%\n通过这个方法，只要大致估计这三个概率，就可以知道第四个概率了，同学们，大家学会了吗","timestamp":1605763828,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782652,"url":"","vote":{}}}